company_name: OHRETAL AGRAR-PRODUKTIONS- UND HANDELSGESELLSCHAFT MBH & CO. KG UTHMÖDEN/SATUELLE
information: The company OHRETAL AGRAR-PRODUKTIONS- UND HANDELSGESELLSCHAFT MBH & CO. KG UTHMÖDEN/SATUELLE, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1992, which operates in the Cereals and grains industry. It is based in Satuelle, Germany.
